Blocks.Text: Notice of Capital Event: Ongoing Expenses
Please be advised that on behalf of the Partnership the Manager is drawing a total of USD
17,392,571.57 from Limited Partners, based on each Limited Partner's percentage of
commitments. As such, in accordance with clause 4.1 of the Limited Partnership Agreement
(the "LPA"), notice is hereby given that a Drawdown is taking place for value date 24 May 2023.
Your share of the amount under the notice is detailed below:
In accordance with clause 5.6 of the LPA, the Manager is issuing this capital event notice for
BANK OF AMERICA N.A., NEW YORK
Please ensure that the remitting bank sends a SWIFT MT103 directly to the beneficiary
Kindly note that in order for incoming payments to be allocated to the correct account it is
essential that the reference is quoted on your payment instruction. It is also a requirement
that funds are sent from an account in the name of the registered investor.
Should you have any questions or concerns regarding this notice, please contact Citco Fund
acting in its capacity as alternative investment fund manager of EQT X (No.2) USD SCSp
